quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  43,61,"Pellet non, ko o anndinorde Darngal. Wota on cikkito fii maggal. Jokkee kam, ko …óuum woni laawol Pocciingol ngol."
  43,62,"Wota seytaane falo on ! tawde pellet, ko o ga√Īo mon …ďanngu…óo."
  43,63,"Nde Iisaa ardunoo e …ďanngu…ói …óin, o maaki: "GooŇč…óii mi ardanii on e √Īee√Īal, e no mi …ďannginirana on yoga e ko luutondir…óon e muu…óum. Haray kulee Allah, …óofto…óon mi."
  43,64,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon. Ndewee Mo. Ko …óuum woni laawol pocciingol ngol"."
  43,65,"Feddeeji …óiin luutondiri hakkunde majji. Bone woodanii …ďen yeddu…ďe, immorde e lepte √Īalaande mu'usuu…óe !"
  43,66,"Hara …ďe habbi si wpnaa nde Darngal ngal ardata …ďe e juhal, hara …ďe so'aa anndude?"
  43,67,"Weldu…ďe …ďeen, nden √Īalnde, yoga ma…ď…ďe ko ayroo…ďe yoga; si wonaa gooŇč…óui…ďe …ďeen."
  43,68,"Ko onon yo jiyaa…ďe Am ! Kulol alanaa on hannde; wonaa on sunotoo…ďe kadi."
  43,69,"…ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óeen, …ďe ngoni jebbilii…ďe,"
  43,70,"naatee ka Aljanna, onon e nanndu…ďe e mon, ho…óon sa…ónee"."
  43,71,"[Golloo…ďe] hino wannginee e ma…ď…ďe, mirannji kaŇčŇče e yeddu…óe; hino ton kadi: kala ko wonkii muuyetee, gite dakmitoo. Hara le, ko on duumotoo…ďe toon."
  43,72,"Ko on ngoni Aljanna mo roninira…óon, sabu ko ko ngollayno…óon."
  43,73,"Hino woodani on toon, muuyantee…ói …óuu…óu…ói, …ói √Īaamoton e mum."